fields.name: Motul DOT 4 RBF 660 Racing 0 Brake Fluid
fields.description: Suitable for all types of hydraulic brake and clutch actuators requiring non-silicone synthetic fluid. Specially designed to resist extreme temperature generated by racing brakes (carbon and ceramic) only allowing a minimal air entrance for brake cooling.
